Start a background sync to pull in the changes from the other repo.

  $ touch $TESTTMP/ccdelay1
  $ CCWAITFILE=$TESTTMP/ccdelay1 hg cloud sync --best-effort > $TESTTMP/bgsync.out 2>&1 &

